I have a Canvas-based chart that's completely invisible to VoiceOver. How do I make the data points accessible?

```swift
Canvas { context, size in
    for point in dataPoints {
        let rect = CGRect(x: point.x * size.width, y: (1 - point.y) * size.height, width: 10, height: 10)
        context.fill(Path(ellipseIn: rect), with: .color(.blue))
    }
}
```
